My heart sincerely goes out to any and EVERYONE affected by the tragedies currently occurring in Gaza. 
I speak for myself only, as an artist with limited resources, there is not much I can do other than donate, and bring awareness. My spirit was touched by all of the coverage of what’s happening, and the only way I can realistically express my concern, care and support, is through music.
With that being said, I strayed away from shooting a real music video with myself In frame, because its not about me, its not about my lifestyle or my image, its about the people of Gaza.
I pray no one takes any offense to anything I said or created with this visual and song. 
I love humanity as a whole, no matter what race, religion or belief. That’s all I am trying to emphasize with this body of work.
I hope this touches everyones spirit who watches or listens.
I hope those of you who are one sided with opinions of who is right and who is wrong in this situation, can somehow find it in yourselves to curse the people actively killing and causing destruction, and stray away from cursing A GROUP OF PEOPLE AS A WHOLE, in response to your concern and pain.
I hope that whoever witnesses the images of this destruction and murder, allow it only to inspire you to love harder, accept others whole heartedly, and always resort to patience and understanding instead of anger and violence.
At the end of the day, we all came from the same place, same God, same beginning. 
No bodies taught God can ever be proven to be the one and only God, we are all one people under the same sky.
So much love an respect for @nadinabdullatif for covering her experiences and being strong enough to strive though it all. Keep fighting 💙 #freepalestine

Ive gotten a few messages from people justifying what’s happening is Gaza, from people that have gone through the same loss of innocent lives on the Israeli side, that pushed them to look at these moments as revenge.
The whole point of the song and message is that no matter who  started what, the politics and the details do not matter, nobody should be getting killed, Israeli people or Palestinian people, those families, those kids, all deserve to see another day.
I 100% sympathize with anyone who lost lives to this mess. 
Just pray for healing 🎯
Politics dont matter, wrong is wrong
Ignorance is Bliss, the less we know about whats going on in this world, the prettier everything seems. When you start to really pay attention to whats happening, the real questions start to come up.
Whats wrong is wrong 🇵🇸 🙏🏼

“Ignorance Is Bliss” is now available on all streaming platforms. 
Thank you to everyone that listened and sympathized, prayer is powerful, and love is real. This song is just a song, the chaos and destruction is still happening. Donate, Repost, Bring awareness, a little can go a long way.. This is just my little input praying it goes a long way 🙏🏼🇵🇸💙
